\noindent\underline{\textbf{Group Quizzes}}:

\noindent
This course follows a strict policy of \textbf{no books, notes, or calculators} on quizzes. However, all of these materials are encouraged when studying and completing in-class or out-of-class practice activities to \textit{check your work} (or for difficult arithmetic which sometimes cannot be avoided).

Quizzes will be completed in small (3-4 person), preassigned groups.
You will take each quiz \textit{individually} for 20-25 minutes.
You will hand it in, and your group will be given another copy of the quiz to complete together.
You will use the remainder of the time to complete the second copy together.
\textbf{Your individual mark will be an average of your individual and group marks.}
The group quiz feedback will be available on D2L.
